Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.27,0:23:00.02,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(1150,1060)\3c&H1C86E5&}キラリ願う
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.02,0:23:01.61,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(1150,1060)\3c&H1C86E5&}どんな希望も
