Dialogue: 1,0:22:41.25,0:22:43.09,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\an3\3c&H764EDB&}敞開教科書的文字上
Dialogue: 1,0:22:43.09,0:22:46.30,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\an3\3c&H764EDB&}字裡行間彷彿隨心起舞
Dialogue: 1,0:22:46.30,0:22:49.76,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\an3\3c&HA82DE4&}踏著步伐走進夢境
Dialogue: 1,0:22:49.76,0:22:53.10,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\an3\3c&HA82DE4&}一躍而起
Dialogue: 1,0:22:53.10,0:22:58.27,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\an1\3c&HC593AF&\pos(150,1000)}未來並非早已注定
